.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783ba4bec65f76459ae97c9205f97037f7be5a95","tid":2044690,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"Monkey 9up"},{"pid":"480c21dfc947672634483c222559836854e4d3ae","tid":2044690,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"入黎恥笑monkey"},{"pid":"dbc3738fe404239417f3a00c57dabb128ed76f49","tid":2044690,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"同民建聯爭取北極有企鵝睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb1efbe72c9b08d2736bedddb3c08117d59ae5d","tid":2044690,"uid":357591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f5f17898118b909f5f065cabb39c643cdfd3f33","tid":2044690,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"澄清「棉」花 與「綿」羊有別 陳振聲自嘲：需要補「眠」！<br />\n<br />\n棉花出在羊身上？貿工部長陳振聲接受訪問時一時口誤，表示棉花產自綿羊。他之後表示，知道訪問出錯後，自己也笑翻了，澄清棉花並不來自綿羊，並押韻表示自己需要補「眠」！<br />\n陳振聲昨天（30日）以英語通過視訊接受媒體訪問，在回答有關國際貿易問題時，他指出新加坡沒有許多原料，必須靠國際貿易才能生存。他以口罩生產為例子，表示「比如棉花（cotton），新加坡沒有綿羊」。<br />\n視頻被放上網後，有網民寫道：「 綿羊產羊毛（wool）。棉花來自植物。」<br />\n陳振聲今天（31）對此在Facebook公開回應，表示在得知自己在談及棉花和綿羊時一時口快後，自己也笑翻了。<br />\n他說：「想告訴看視頻的人（尤其是小朋友），棉花不是出自綿羊身上，而是植物！」<br />\n陳振聲說，過去幾個星期，一直在想可以用什麼替代品來生產口罩，「可惜的是，新加坡沒有棉花，也沒有綿羊（sheep）。」<br />\n文末，他也用英語押韻表示：「與此同時，我需要去補眠（sleep）。。。」<br />\n陳振聲這則玩味帖文已獲超過3000人點贊，不少網民留言表示小錯誤無傷大雅，有人寫道「能夠自嘲真的很棒。歡笑是讓我們維持好心情的良藥。」也有人說：「部長，不要放在心上。你也是人。好好休息」，「最重要是部長和他的團隊能為我國帶來投資。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5s2aj0E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5s2aj0E.jpg&h=9d34f7ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/chan-chun-sing-sheep-cotton-1148251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8world.com%2Fnews%2Fsingapore%2Farticle%2Fchan-chun-sing-sheep-cotton-1148251&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdCLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=c781211a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/chan-chun-sing-sheep-cotton-1148251</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"呢條友（陳振聲）原來真係白痴嚟！"},{"pid":"ddf0610407dc8201e78f9195bfca4d53997d4f59","tid":2044690,"uid":17125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWAK9yP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWAK9yP.jpg&h=a56e15d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gYAwNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gYAwNb.jpg&h=2f540507&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6586287c3446846158a818cfc8fa785ee4bfe4e","tid":2044690,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"Monkeys dont understand where is the cotton from<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4944113a9efe1ce87139e5114cbf67b8204fcc2c","tid":2044690,"uid":3768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb29a552732e19f23348e3376f642ca305e183ee","tid":2044690,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be775fcd49d790f62fc7828e90aafc38be8af8dc","tid":2044690,"uid":21545,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"MSMD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:23:10.000Z","msg":"monkey sick monkey die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1256aa855100de2761fd62df9282cfd4778d61","tid":2044690,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"綿花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />